description: Fork of  zspine/deliver_sm.py, updated to work with changes in Jasmin SMS since the original was created + fixes a rabbitmq bug. This script will take a submit_sm PDU, send an OK back to the originator whilst replaying it to jasmin as a deliver_sm, effectively converting a submit_sm to deliver_sm. Also will send back a DELIVRD DLR!
